# Verification Documents Upload Directory

This directory stores company verification documents uploaded by admins.

## File Naming
- Pattern: `doc-<timestamp>-<random>.<ext>`
- Example: `doc-1729234567890-123456789.pdf`

## Accepted File Types
- PDF (.pdf)
- Images (.jpg, .jpeg, .png)
- Word Documents (.doc, .docx)

## Size Limit
- Maximum: 5MB per file

## Security
- Admin-only upload access
- File type validation (MIME)
- Unique filename generation
- No executable files allowed
